## Command Reference

All commands: `python -m cli [--db <path>] <command> <subcommand> [options]`

### Workflow
```bash
workflow create --title "..." [--source-file <path>]
workflow list
workflow import <W-ID> --structure '<json>'
workflow import <W-ID> --structure-file <path.json>
workflow delete <W-ID>
workflow set-order <T-ID> <T-ID> ...
workflow set-parallel --group <name> <T-ID> ...
workflow add-dep <T-ID> --depends-on <T-ID> ...
workflow show
workflow next
workflow current
```

### Epic / Task
```bash
epic create --title "..." [--description "..."]
epic list | show <E-ID> | update <E-ID> --status <status> | delete <E-ID>

task create --parent <E-ID or T-ID> --title "..."
task list [--epic <E-ID>] [--status <status>]
task show <T-ID>
task update <T-ID> --status <todo|in_progress|interrupted|done|cancelled>
task update <T-ID> --status interrupted --interrupt "reason"
task delete <T-ID>
```

### Plan (partial updates to existing workflow)
```bash
plan update --changes '<json>' [--workflow <W-ID>]
# JSON: {"create": [...], "update": [...], "delete": [...]}
```

### Operations
```bash
op start <T-ID> --platform <claude_code|gemini_cli>
op progress <T-ID> --summary "..."
op complete <T-ID> --summary "..."
op error <T-ID> --summary "..."
op interrupt <T-ID> --summary "..."
op log [--task <T-ID>]
```

### Query / Status
```bash
query show [--workflow <W-ID>]
query status
query tasks [--status <status>]
```

### Objective
```bash
objective create --title "..." --milestone "..."
objective create --title "..." --due-date YYYY-MM-DD
objective list
objective update <O-ID> --status done
```

### Settings
```bash
setting set <key> <value> [--desc "..."]
setting get <key>
setting list
setting delete <key>
```

### Project (rollback / restart)
```bash
project checkpoint [--note "..."]
project checkpoint list
project rollback --checkpoint <id>
project restart [--clear-ops]
```
